author: webkinz19
title: I remember this set
review:
I liked this set when I was like 2. Good for parts duplo parts like the bush and flowers but the figs are not good so if you ever saw this set and you wanted duplo parts get but only for cheep price maybe get.

  • pros                                                    
  • tree
  • flowers
  • bush
  • the few bricks you get
  • cons
  • figs are not good
  • pooh bear is not a good idea
  • sign is not cool
  • needs more bricks

So maybe buy it.
